                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On the evening of November 24 the <hi rend="italic">Ad Hoc</hi> Committee
                    rejected by a 29 to 12 vote, with 14 abstentions, the third draft resolution of
                    Subcommittee <pb facs="1299" n="1285" xml:id="pg_1285"/> 2 containing the
                    unitary plan for Palestine; see <gloss target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>(II), <hi
                        rend="italic">Ad Hoc Committee</hi>, page 206. The text of the resolution is
                    printed <hi rend="italic">ibid.</hi>, page 302.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
